【Two Hearts】\c[27]A wicked change occurs in Seria...

\F[36]\AA[F]I'm sorry for what I said earlier. I was just
frustrated...

\F[36]\AA[F]I've heard about the situation. Besides, I don't like
\c[27]him\c. There's someone else I'm thinking about.

\F[10]\AA[F]I just want to safely leave this place with that
person. Please, understand!

I've been showered with abuse many times. \c[14] Especially this
past year \c.

Every time that happens, Lady Sadi comforts me. So, I'm not
bothered by it. Me.
\F[17]\AA[F](She seems a bit... her eyes look vacant...)
But I do want to become friends with you again, Seri-chan.

You're incredibly honest and brave... just like a protagonist. If
I were in the same situation, I'd be broken-hearted.
Hey, as a sign of friendship, I'll teach you one magic spell.

I think you'll fail many times at first, but with your incredible
magical power, Seri-chan, you'll be able to do it soon.
The place is like this... the incantation is like this....

\F[10]\AA[F]It's difficult, but it really feels like being a
magician.
Well... \c[27] I remember a lot of other things too \c.
Do you understand if I say clairvoyance?
How about looking it up in a book on the first floor?
\c[14]Clairvoyance\c is the effect of having a far-seeing eye.
I particularly want the current Seria-chan...\c[14] I think \c♡
Why don't you look it up in a book on the first floor?
